                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <p>"纵向目标"和“横向目标”的区别：前者基于一般大众认可，后者基于个人兴趣使然。追求纵向杰出成就较易引起同侪竞争，而横向杰出成就容易获得同侪赞赏，因此横向成就比纵向成就更让同侪觉得“有面子”。但是，纵向失败要比横向失败更让同侪觉得“没面子”。</p>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
</span>
</div>

                  </div>
                <div class="pl col-time">
                  <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/44568614/#comments">回应</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
                  2017-06-04 15:50
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
  </ul>
  

      
